Oh, it's, it's okay.

01:41:12.142 --> 01:41:14.442
Well, this'll cure
what ails you.

01:41:14.542 --> 01:41:17.342
- Really?
- Oh, yeah.

01:41:17.342 --> 01:41:19.442
How's your butt?

