wouldn't take a check.

01:41:59.242 --> 01:42:02.042
- So how'd you come up with the money?
- I ain't tellin'.

01:42:02.142 --> 01:42:04.642
- Pepper!
- Nope. My secret.

01:42:04.742 --> 01:42:08.042
